provided by the NMFS Office of Protected Resources for information only.  Reference should be made to the official report of the Act in the United States Code.

</EM>
<P><A HREF="mmpacred.html">Credits and Conditions</A>

<CENTER><H1>The Marine Mammal Protection Act of 1972, as
AmendedThrough 1994</H1></CENTER>

<P>To protect marine mammals; to establish a Marine Mammal
Commission; for other purposes.

<P><EM>Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives
of the United States of America in Congress assembled,</EM> That
this Act, with the following table of contents, may be cited as
the "Marine Mammal Protection Act of 1972".

<CENTER><H2>TABLE OF CONTENTS</H2></CENTER>
<CENTER><H3>Subchapter I - Generally</H3></CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="mmpa002.html">Sec. 2 (16 USC 1361)</A> - Findings and declaration of policy
