<CENTER><H3>Sec. 4. Effective Date</H3></CENTER>

<P>The provisions of this Act shall take effect upon the expiration
of the sixty-day period following the date of its enactment
[December 21, 1972].

<P><A HREF="mmpa101.html">Go to next section</A>
<P><A HREF="#Top of page">Return to top of page</A>

