<CENTER><H3>Sec. 408 (16 USC 1421g) Authorization of appropriations</H3></CENTER>

<P>There is authorized to be appropriated--
<UL>
<P>(1) to the Secretary for carrying out this subchapter (other
than sections 1421d and 1421f of this title) $250,000 for each of
fiscal years 1993 and 1994;

<P>(2) to the Secretary for carrying out section 1421f of this
title, $250,000 for each of fiscal years 1993 and 1994; and 

<P>(3) to the Fund, $500,000 for fiscal year 1993.
</UL>
