<TABLE WIDTH=80% CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT>KMPC listeners can win a wide variety of prizes just 
for listening. Giveaways on "The Peter Tilden Show with Tracey Miller" 
offer listeners great opportunities to win exciting evenings and 
activities all around town!</TD></TR> </TABLE>
<P>


<H2><!-- Anchor Link Tag -->
<A HREF="#GIVEAWAYS">Listen and Win!</A></H2>

<H2><A HREF="#RULES">The Rules</A></H2>

</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
