<IMG WIDTH=90% HEIGHT=3 BORDER=0  SRC="../gifs/redBar.1.gif">  

<!-- Anchor Point Tag -->
<A NAME="GIVEAWAYS"><P></A>

<TABLE WIDTH=80% CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0>

<TR><TD><B><FONT SIZE=5>

ROD LURIE'S PIONEER LASER DISC CONTEST</FONT></B></TD></TR>

<TR><TD><P>

	Hey video laser disc fans check-out this great Pioneer contest. <P>

	<P>We're giving away two spectacular Pioneer laser discs - The Beatles Anthology and an 
Indiana Jones package featuring Raiders of the Lost Ark and Indiana Jones and the Temple of 
Doom.<P>

	<P>If you're a Beatles fan, or if you like a good documentary film, you'll love The Beatles 
Anthology. Of course, the Indiana Jones series are classic, and these particular laser discs are 
simply pristine! It's almost makes it seem like you're watching the movie for the first time.<P>

	<P>So, <A HREF=form.htm>enter to win</A>. The contest ends September 8, 1996. However, 
please note that the contest is open to Los Angeles, Orange County, San Bernardino, Riverside, 
Ventura and San Diego residents only. <P>

	<P>Don't forget to email me your picks for the <A HREF="../Rod_Lurie/list.htm">
Top Ten All-time Best Movies </A>.<P>
<P>
<CENTER><A HREF=form.htm>CLICK HERE TO REGISTER FOR THE CONTEST</A></CENTER>
<P>
</TD></TR> </TABLE>
<P>

<TABLE  WIDTH=80%  CELLSPACING=5  CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0>
<TR><TD><B><FONT SIZE=5>
PETER AND TRACEY GIVEAWAYS</FONT></B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD><B>Monday - Friday, 5:30 a.m. - 9 a.m.</B></TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Giveaways on the "Peter Tilden with  Tracey Miller Show" consist 
of a wide variety of prizes.  The two pull from this grab bag of 
prizes when they feel "the mood" to reward listeners for their smarts, 
charisma or "butt kissing" ability.
</TD></TR>
</TD></TR></TABLE>
<P>

<A NAME=RULES>
<TABLE CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0 WIDTH=80%>
<TR><TD><H2>710 TALK / KMPC CONTEST RULES</H2>

710 TALK / KMPC contests are open to all listeners.  No purchase is 
necessary to enter station contests.  Employees of DISNEY / ABC, Inc. 
Incorporated and their immediate families are not eligible to win 
prizes.  Listeners can win only once every 60 days.


  Official rules for specific contests are available by writing to 710 
TALK / KMPC, P.O. Box 710, Los Angeles, California 90016. </TD></TR>
</TABLE>
