<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>Tracey Miller</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=ffffff  TEXT=#000000 LINK=#FF0000 VLINK=#FF0000 ALINK=#0000FF>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
	<IMG SRC=tm1.gif ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 VSPACE=40></A>
	<H1>Tracey Miller</H1>
	<H3>Monday-Friday<BR>5 - 9 a.m.</H3>



                   <P>Tracey Miller has been a successful radio broadcaster for the past 15 years. Her sharp sense of humor, stand-out
                   radio voice and journalistic skills have made her one of the premier talk show hosts in Los Angeles.<P>

                   <P>Tracey has proven that women have a voice in drive-time radio. Prior to joining  KMPC-AM,
                   Tracey co-hosted a morning talk show on KFI-AM. In addition, she hosted her own successful entertainment talk
                   show, Tracey Miller's Celebrity File, which combined in-studio guests, funny gossip, and movie and television
                   reviews.<P>

		   <P>Tracey is an award-winning broadcast journalist. She has been honored with first-place awards for her radio work
                   as reporter, writer and editor by the Radio and Television News Association (four Golden Mike Awards),
                   Associated Press, United Press International, Sigma Delta Chi and the National Association of Press Women.<P>


<BR><BR>
<CENTER><A HREF="http://www.cybershows.com/"><IMG SRC=smog.gif BORDER=0></A><BR><A HREF="http://www.cybershows.com/">Smog Check II</A></CENTER>


</BLOCKQUOTE>


<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<BR>

