<IMG SRC=XH.jpg ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 VSPACE=40>
<H1>Xavier Hermosillo</H1>
<H3>Monday - Friday<BR> 7 - 9 p.m.</H3>
<P>
<P>Every week night, Latino activist and businessman <B>Xavier Hermosillo 
</B>takes over the microphone at 710 Talk. A respected entrepreneur, 
political leader and journalist, Xavier draws upon his varied 
experiences to drive his show. Known to his
 devout listeners as "<B>The X-MAN</B>,"	 Xavier presents a program that is 
fast-paced, controversial and <I>definitely </I>politically incorrect.<P>
