<TR><TD>
<P>
                   

<P>We asked for your choices and here they are. The best English language films of all time - according to you. These are in 
rank order. To qualify for the list, the film had to receive at least SIXTY-FIVE points.  I welcome you to continue 
E-mailing me your top ten. The list will be dynamic, changing from week to week.  Of course, the qualifying number of votes 
will go up with each passing week.  For now, however.......</P>

