<DOCHDR>
http://www.710talkkmpc.com:80/Rod_Lurie/best_film.htm 204.31.162.112 19970111200216 text/html 4279
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 11 Jan 1997 20:03:30 GMT
