<P>
         

<P>Okay, folks... You have seen my picks for the ten best male performances ever (if you haven't, check them out).  Now, here 
is how your picks have fallen into place. We have two lists. One  are the actors who got the most combined votes. The second 
is the performance specific list. If you haven't sent me your top ten, by all means, do so.    E-mail me from the bar below. 
This list will by  dynamic, changing every few weeks or so.  This is the list as of the second week of November, 1996.<P>

