<TD WIDTH=85% ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=BOTTOM><!-- Anchor Point Tag -->
<FONT SIZE=6><B>CALIFORNIA ANGELS</B></FONT>

</TD></TR>
</TABLE>

<TABLE CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0  WIDTH=90%>
<TR><TD  WIDTH=10%></TD>
<TD><BR>
<FONT SIZE=5><B>The Angels  Broadcast Team</B></FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE=4><B>710 TALK / KMPC brings you the California 
Angels.</B></FONT><BR>


<IMG WIDTH=156 ALIGN=LEFT  VALIGN=TOP HEIGHT=216 VSPACE=4 HSPACE=10 BORDER=2 ALT="Bob Starr" SRC="bobStarr.1.jpg"> 
<P> 
You will hear all the spectacular action during the entire California 
Angels season.  Bob Starr and Mario Impemba team up to give you  
play-by-play action and excitement.  Bob Starr is entering his 40th year 
in broadcasting, with 25 years of Major League Baseball experience 
behind the mike. <IMG WIDTH=156 ALIGN=RIGHT  VALIGN=BOTTOM  HEIGHT=216 
VSPACE=4 HSPACE=10 BORDER=2 ALT="Mario Impemba" SRC="mario.1.jpg"> <P>
Entering his 11th year in broadcasting, Mario Impemba joins his partner 
for their third season together.  Prior to announcing for the California 
Angels, 
Mario spent four seasons as the play-by-play voice for the Tucson 
Toros of the Pacific Coast League. <P>

</TD></TR>

<TR><TD></TD><TD>
</TABLE>

<A NAME="Schedule">
<TABLE CELLSPACING=4 CELLPADDING=1 BORDER=0 WIDTH=80%>

<TR><TD COLSPAN=5 ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=5><B>
