<TITLE>KMPC Talent: Tom Leykis</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=ffffff  TEXT=#000000 LINK=#FF0000 VLINK=#CC0000 ALINK=#0000FF>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<IMG SRC=bigTL.jpg ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 VSPACE=40>
<H1>Tom Leykis</H1>
<H3>Monday-Friday<BR>3 - 7 p.m.</H3>
<P>
<P>There's no doubt that Tom is one of a kind. As <I>The Los Angeles 
Times</I> reported, people don't have luke-warm feelings about Tom 
Leykis.	 He brings a unique dimension to the talk radio format with a 
cutting-edge style that draws a new and younger
 audience. In Tom's words, it's talk radio you can dance to.  He taps 
into a guest list of Hollywood's elite and outrageous who appear on his 
show. Guests vary from actors, comedians and rock stars to politicians 
and opinion-makers. There's no telling 
what particular topic he may choose to arouse his audience.
