<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>KMPC Talent: Bob Heckler</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=ffffff TEXT=#000000 LINK=#FF0000 VLINK=#CC0000 ALINK=#0000FF>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<IMG SRC=BH.gif ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 VSPACE=40 BORDER=2>
<H1>Bob Heckler</H1>
<H3>Monday - Friday<BR> 9 a.m. to Noon</H3>
<P>
 If you want a debatable, fiery and conservative radio host, then
 KMPC's Bob Heckler is what you are looking for.  Bob is the host with 
the most in terms of in-your-face,
 "no-looking-back" talk. He has a history of being the "black sheep" of the
 airwaves. His career began in Denver, where he was the host of the only
 secular talk show on Christian radio. Bob's energizing and fast-paced 710
 TALK / KMPC show covers current events with a significant right-wing
 feel to it. So if you can handle being shocked, and having your ideology
 chewed up without losing it, tune in Bob Heckler on KMPC.

<P>

