<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>KMPC Talent: Michael Reagan</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=ffffff  TEXT=#000000 LINK=#FF0000 VLINK=#CC0000 ALINK=#0000FF>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<IMG SRC=reagan.jpg ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=20 VSPACE=40>
<H1>Michael Reagan</H1>
<H3>Monday-Friday<BR>3 - 7 p.m.</H3>
<P>
<P>
Michael Reagan, son of President Ronald Reagan, joins the KMPC line-up with a national talk show 
that focuses on Congress, the Executive Branch and politics. His show features one-on-one 
interviews with influential newsmakers, congressional leaders and opinion makers.<P>
<P>
Michael adds humor, wit and warmth while addressing some of the most important political and 
social issues with callers from across the nation. Reagan broadcasts his KMPC Talk Show live 
from Los Angeles and always looks to his fellow Southern Californians for input and lively 
debate.<P>
<P>
Michael began his radio career as a guest host on KABC Talkradio in Los Angeles. His L.A. 
appearances helped pave the way for a full-time talk show in San Diego and ultimately a national 
talk program.  Since then, he has built a loyal national audience.<P>
<P>
Prior to his radio career, Reagan was active in power boat racing, which earned him world 
records and raised millions of dollars for various charities. In addition, he is an author of a 
best-selling autobiography, On the Outside Looking In, and was one of two Americans named 
Honorary Members of the 104th Congress.<P>
<P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
CLICK HERE TO BE CONNECTED TO MICHAEL REAGAN'S WEB SITE<BR>
<A HREF="http://www.reagan.com">http://www.reagan.com</A> 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR CLEAR=ALL></BR>
