<DOCNO>WT11-B05-176</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA071-000449-B026-305</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.childhub.ch:80/webpub/csechome/2176.htm 193.135.156.14 19970120225514 text/html 6355
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.13
